title: Goblet, ca. 1810–15
provenance: M.H. Impey, 172 Walton St. London, S.W. 3, purchased (8-8-69) by WPW.
description: Funnel shaped bowl with drawn stem and plain circular, slightly domed foot.Wheel engraved around upper part with garland joining bows interspersed with 8 point stars.

tombstone.epitaph:
Goblet, ca. 1810–15.
ca. 1810–15. glass. Bequest of Walter Phelps Warren. 1986-61-207.
